Package: libido-0.1-0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: indicator-sound (<< 0.3.7 )
Description: widgets and other objects used for indicators
 Ido is a shared library providing extra GTK+ menu items for display
 in system indicators
 .
 This package contains shared libraries to be used by GTK+ 2 applications.

